full_affiliations: ["Valerie Satkoske MSW, PhD, is the Director of Ethics for Wheeling Hospital in Wheeling, WV, and the ethics consultant for The Diocese of Wheeling-Charleston and the Rural Emergency Trauma Institute of West Virginia.
